column2: SELECT TOP # /* PhotoObj table parameters*/  p.objid,round(p.ra,#) as ra,round(p.dec,#) as dec,round(p.u,#) as PhotoOb_u,round(p.g,#) as PhotoOb_g,round(p.r,#) as PhotoOb_r,  round(p.i,#) as err_i,round(p.err_u,#) as err_u, round(p.err_g,#) as err_g, round(p.err_r,#) as err_r, round(P.err_i,#) as err_i, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#Err_r as   PhotoOb_i,round(p.z,#) as PhotoObj_z, p.type, /*specObj table parameters*/  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subClass, round(s.z,#) as spec_redshift,  round(s.zErr,#) as spec_redshift_Err,round(s.zWarning,#) as Spec_redshift_Warning, /* Photomtric redshift table parameters*/  round(pz.z,#) As Photo_Z, round(pz.zErr,#) AS Photo_Err  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID=p.objid
